title: Football Manager 2015 editor
description:
This is the official FM 2015 editor that comes with the original game. Make no confusion with the in-game real time editor, this is just the regular editor that runs outside the game and can edit the database.

How to use: Just place it next to the game's folder (for example, if your FM is in program files, place the editor's folder there as well).

It's been tested and fully working. Please share it further
